event.title: Software Freedom Day booth in Vienna

body.p: The Vienna fellowship group will hold a booth in the very busy city centre of Vienna on the corner of the Mariahilfer Sta√üe and the Museumsquartier. From 10am until 7pm we will be answering questions at our information desk and giving out leaflets and live CDs from different free operating systems. Many of them with a specially produced CD-edition identifying the FSFE fellowship as provider of the copies. We will bring notebook computers as well to show interested passers-by how well Free Software works and how good it looks.
